OL,3,CWatchdog brands children's jail 'most
OL,4,Cviolent prison in the country'
OL,6,FA troubled children's jail has been
OL,7,Fbranded the most violent prison in the
OL,8,Fcountry by a watchdog.
OL,10,FChief inspector of prisons Charlie
OL,11,FTaylor said he was "very concerned" at
OL,12,Fhow much Feltham A young offender
OL,13,Finstitution (YOI) ` which holds
OL,14,Fchildren aged between 15 and 18 ` had
OL,15,Fdeteriorated in the past two years
OL,16,Fafter figures indicated there was six
OL,17,Ftimes more violence at the west London
OL,18,Fsite than at one of the most violent
OL,19,Fadult prisons in England and Wales.
