OL,3,CWatchdog brands children's jail 'most
OL,4,Cviolent prison in the country'
OL,6,FThe watchdog found there were 410
OL,7,Fviolent incidents at Feltham A within
OL,8,Fa 12-month period from 84 children,
OL,9,Fequating to a rate of 488 incidents
OL,10,Fper 100 children.
OL,12,FBy contrast, the latest inspection of
OL,13,FHMP Bedford ` one of the most violent
OL,14,Fadult prisons ` found the rate of
OL,15,Fviolence was calculated at 80.6
OL,16,Fincidents per 100 prisoners.
