OL,3,CWatchdog brands children's jail 'most
OL,4,Cviolent prison in the country'
OL,6,FIn a report published on Tuesday, Mr
OL,7,FTaylor said: "It was disappointing to
OL,8,Freturn to find there had been a
OL,9,Fdeterioration in standards with levels
OL,10,Fof violence now the highest of any
OL,11,Fprison in the country."
OL,13,FInspectors found high levels of
OL,14,Fviolence and rising self-harm when
OL,15,Fthey visited Feltham A in March.
OL,17,FIncidents of disorder had "tripled"
OL,18,Fsince the last inspection, with the
OL,19,Flatest report detailing the volatile
OL,20,Fsituation the watchdog found behind
OL,21,Fbars.
