OL,3,CWatchdog brands children's jail 'most
OL,4,Cviolent prison in the country'
OL,6,FThere had been a "dramatic increase"
OL,7,Fin the number of assaults and serious
OL,8,Fincidents last summer which led to the
OL,9,Feducation block being shut down for
OL,10,Fseveral weeks.
OL,12,FRather than attending lessons with
OL,13,Fchildren who had similar interests and
OL,14,Fabilities, boys were assigned to
OL,15,Fclasses based on which other inmates
OL,16,Fthey would not fight with, according
OL,17,Fto the findings.
