OL,3,CWatchdog brands children's jail 'most
OL,4,Cviolent prison in the country'
OL,6,FThe watchdog also raised "major"
OL,7,Fconcerns about the "worryingly
OL,8,Fprolonged" segregation of some of the
OL,9,Fchild prisoners, highlighting how
OL,10,Fseven children had been separated for
OL,11,Fmore than 50 days, and two of them for
OL,12,Fmore than 100.
OL,14,FMr Taylor's report is the latest in a
OL,15,Fstring of concerns raised about the
OL,16,Fhigh-profile YOI over the years.
