OL,3,CWatchdog brands children's jail 'most
OL,4,Cviolent prison in the country'
OL,6,FThe Government halted sending children
OL,7,Fto Feltham A in 2019 when the then
OL,8,Fchief inspector of prisons demanded
OL,9,Fimmediate action over an
OL,10,F"extraordinary" plunge in safety
OL,11,Flevels. It came after a report found a
OL,12,Fsurge in violence and self-harm at the
OL,13,Fjail.
OL,15,FMr Taylor added: "We were very
OL,16,Fconcerned to find how Feltham A had
OL,17,Fdeteriorated in the past two years,
OL,18,Fbut it is to the credit of the
OL,19,Fgovernor and her leadership team that
OL,20,Fthere were signs that they had managed
OL,21,Fto arrest this decline.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@OO]wD@ROU
