OL,3,CWatchdog brands children's jail 'most
OL,4,Cviolent prison in the country'
OL,6,F"Frontline staff, meanwhile, were a
OL,7,Freal asset to the jail and had managed
OL,8,Fto maintain impressively positive and
OL,9,Fsupportive relationships with even the
OL,10,Fmost challenging children in their
OL,11,Fcare despite the violence around them."
OL,13,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,14,Fsaid: "The criminal justice system is
OL,15,Fin crisis and as this report clearly
OL,16,Fshows, this is placing great strain on
OL,17,Fthe youth estate.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@gO]vD@GOU
