OL,3,CWatchdog brands children's jail 'most
OL,4,Cviolent prison in the country'
OL,6,F"As the Chief Inspector recognises in
OL,7,Fhis report, the governor and frontline
OL,8,Fstaff are now making every effort to
OL,9,Fdrive improvements and reduce
OL,10,Fviolence. But we know there is much
OL,11,Fmore to do and we are committed to
OL,12,Fincreasing the support these children
OL,13,Fneed to turn their lives around."
